				</div>
							<div class="featured-item-story">
					<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/seven-holiday-romance-novels-to-keep-warm-with-this-winter/" title="Seven Holiday Romance Novels to Keep Warm With This Winter">Seven Holiday Romance Novels to Keep Warm With This Winter</a></h2>
